				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>Whenever a creature is hit by the abyssal rotfiend's skullsplitter Strike, that creature must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:33] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature is unaffected and immune for 1 minute</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 2}</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 3} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF]{Paralyzed} until the end of their next turn.</p>",
