					"value": "<p>The abyssal rotfiend targets a single creature it can see within 60 feet, dealing @Damage[8d6[mental]] damage. Target creature must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:33] save. The abyssal rotfiend can't use Abscess Of The Mind for [[/gmr 1d4 #Duration]]{1d4 rounds}</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature is unaffected</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the creature takes half damage</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AdPVz7rbaVSRxHFg]{Fascinated} by the rotfiend until the end of their next turn</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> the creature takes double damage and its fascinated for 1 minute</p>",
