					"value": "<p><strong>Frequency </strong>Once per day</p><hr /><p>The abyssal rotfiend creates a dark miasma of despair and psychic energy in a @Template[burst|distance:20] within 100 feet that lasts for 1 minute. Every creature that starts their turn inside the emanation takes @Damage[8d6[mental]] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:33|basic] save). If a creature ends its turn while inside the miasma, the abyssal rotfiend has a +1 status bonus to hit against that creature until the end of their next turn. The abyssal rotfiend can [[/act sustain]] the spell up to 1 minute, and as part of the [[/act sustain]] action, it can move the miasma by 10 feet in every direction within 100 fet of it.</p>",
